Property.Value:
BEGIN SET NOCOUNT ON;
SELECT [w].[WaveformID], [w].[SampleCount], [w].[TypeName], [w].[TypeID], [w].[Samples], [w].[Compressed], [w].[TopicSessionID], [w].[StartTimeUTC], [w].[EndTimeUTC], [w].[CreateDate] FROM [dbo].[Waveform] AS [w] WHERE [w].[TopicSessionID] = @TopicSessionID AND [w].[StartTimeUTC] >= @StartTime AND [w].[EndTimeUTC] <= @EndTime; END;
